          Our work is published in leading peer-reviewed journals and presented at international conferences.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="https://scholar.google.de/citations?user=kGQy6cYAAAAJ"
            target="_blank"
